Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.30,0:00:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.50,0:00:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.97,0:00:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.51,0:00:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.62,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.83,0:00:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.63,0:00:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.91,0:01:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.35,0:01:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.02,0:01:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.66,0:01:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.36,0:01:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.25,0:01:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团为了统治地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.42,0:01:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以无人操纵MD\N为主要军力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,创立新生OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.89,0:01:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.02,0:01:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于反对财团的功利主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.53,0:01:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的所有权力被夺去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.10,0:01:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,组织形态出现改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.77,0:01:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但藉着MD的高性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们快速地扩大了支配地域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.41,0:02:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于宇宙卫星认同了财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.91,0:02:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,财团下令杀死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.58,0:02:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全孤立的钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.65,0:02:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对他们来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.78,0:02:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,历史的洪流继续不断倒流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.82,0:02:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要比任何人都战斗到底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.73,0:02:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比地球上的任何人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.96,0:02:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比山克王国的莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.17,0:02:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十一话\N[玻璃的山克王国]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.25,0:02:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.49,0:02:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在校舍的理事长室等你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.12,0:02:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后我们自己去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.49,0:02:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不懂说谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.16,0:02:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而要我说谎的角色不适合你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.30,0:03:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要回钢弹后，我就马上离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.50,0:03:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊!希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个国家需要钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.44,0:03:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，那件事一定要保密啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.61,0:03:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜不需要钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，需要它保护公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要明白，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.19,0:03:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好少见!是男生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那两人从哪个国家来的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在前面的是佣人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.33,0:03:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年轻的保镖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我作为这所学园的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.25,0:03:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎两位入学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.11,0:03:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛\N你没收到学园的校服吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.99,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不打算久留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成在这国家的事后\N我就离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.76,0:04:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前钢弹驾驶员，OZ宇宙军特士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.57,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在L2E区0X地点下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐告诉我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.80,0:04:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她说这个人也很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.28,0:04:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国也有朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已得到他们协助搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.51,0:04:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.45,0:04:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以留在这国家\N直至找到他吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.72,0:04:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹驾驶员在山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.45,0:04:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不妥吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.99,0:04:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我无必要故意夸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.86,0:04:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但躲躲藏藏，问题也不会解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.76,0:04:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，这个国家没有战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.56,0:04:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.53,0:04:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在这里也是一个普通男生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.62,0:04:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我衷心赞赏你这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.22,0:05:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改变命运的英明决断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向各位介绍两位新朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.76,0:05:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是卡特尔‧拿巴伯‧温拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.80,0:05:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流星作战，终于开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会随时和你联络告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击的目标和敌人的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.94,0:05:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.91,0:05:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后，你就从速行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，给你取个代号吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我决定借用宇宙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平领导人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.75,0:05:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.46,0:05:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是希洛‧唯，多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全是女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为男孩认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.98,0:06:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是靠对话不能解决一切吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是男女的分别吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.18,0:06:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女性也有喜欢战斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不介意\N可以做我的对手吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听过你的自我介绍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.53,0:06:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我还未自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫桃乐丝‧卡塔罗尼亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.80,0:06:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和罗姆斐拉的干部有血缘关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.11,0:06:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但莉莉娜殿下接纳我为同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想和你做好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，我不可以不坚强呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你讨厌吧，软弱的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.16,0:06:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某地方有一个和你同名的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.96,0:06:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个人为了令宇宙得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.46,0:06:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豁出性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.13,0:06:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后成为宇宙的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,许多人因为他的死而悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.34,0:07:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愤而发誓要报复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.24,0:07:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一个同名的人\N也正在成为传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.58,0:07:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.42,0:07:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有最高天份和力量的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.42,0:07:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也会为和平而战吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.19,0:07:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也会为了\N变成传说而丧命吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.80,0:07:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传说中的骑士不会故意打输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.11,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了躲藏而输给女性这等事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.24,0:07:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.08,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坚强、高尚、猛烈地燃烧生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后才步向死亡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.75,0:07:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应该能创造更伟大的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.45,0:07:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.14,0:08:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然厉害\N但是，我也很了得吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.61,0:08:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不明白你说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除我之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来还有两个希洛‧唯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他打算隐瞒身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.86,0:08:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样\N我们永远一起在山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多多指教，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你召唤我吗?莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才，罗姆斐拉来电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请求批准在山克王国内战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么回事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被OZ追杀的特列斯派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.18,0:08:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃进了南部的森林地带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我刚才已经叫他们马上离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.48,0:08:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们离开，能逃得掉吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们好像有伤兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也可以向敌人投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是本国的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有伤兵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.63,0:09:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉的追击部队正在迫近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.26,0:09:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再去命令特列斯派的部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退到国境之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.03,0:09:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.97,0:09:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帕根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.00,0:09:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能让他们暂时投奔本国吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，罗姆斐拉也会停止攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.64,0:09:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也知道罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.48,0:09:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当山克王国是眼中钉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不能把伤兵交给他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想为了避免混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做出违反人道的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你明白，诺茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.49,0:09:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就那样和特列斯派联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.10,0:09:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!\N想不到要逃进山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.67,0:09:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新生OZ的攻击好巧妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.14,0:09:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们被迫至走投无路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们真可笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.68,0:09:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然被罗姆斐拉利用\N为攻击山克王国的藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，我们不能慢吞吞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续下去会为这国家带来麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.22,0:10:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长!以你的身体状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.09,0:10:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你离开不了国境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦是为了不沾污\N特列斯派的声誉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一定要离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.53,0:10:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特尉，山克王国有联络来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.10,0:10:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们说莉莉娜公主有指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是山克王国的近卫兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路克蕾琪亚‧诺茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.77,0:10:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本国准备暂时收容各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请各位遵照公主的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解除武装投奔本国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信那是最好的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队内有很多伤兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.42,0:10:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本来我们乐于接受你们的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.06,0:10:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们被赶进这里是个陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.43,0:10:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ不会就此了事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.76,0:10:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陷阱?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.70,0:10:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们截断退路之后却不来进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.53,0:10:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在应该轻易就能消灭我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.94,0:10:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他们正要求增援部队前来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.07,0:10:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗无可避免会牵连山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.94,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，我们一定要离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.71,0:11:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里有很多\N和平主义国家的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ最近的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是想藉着在本国发动战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.42,0:11:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令和平主义国家感到不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.49,0:11:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打乱各国的团结   我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.73,0:11:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始终不能为了我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令山克王国出现弱点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.63,0:11:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主的好意我心领了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算怎办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进一步的情报\N也会令你们有麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想终止通讯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.41,0:11:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后交给我们处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.95,0:11:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了，祝各位好运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好见死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原谅我，为了这国家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.99,0:11:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不!这是为了未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.67,0:12:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵的机动战士吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.40,0:12:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国再度来电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.24,0:12:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐吓他们吧   不要紧\N接过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.01,0:12:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.41,0:12:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收容投奔本国的特列斯派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.68,0:12:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你们进一步入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会直接向财团抗议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.65,0:12:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我收到的情报有若干不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派为了逃过我们的追击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.86,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占据了山克王国的中心部躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他们进入市区前攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我们给予和平的协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.77,0:13:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派没有攻击的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.27,0:13:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们已经那样表明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们表明了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.77,0:13:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我们更加不能相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.47,0:13:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通讯完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.84,0:13:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为有可能被敌人偷听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.45,0:13:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能这样\N请收回承命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把特列斯派赶进市区增加伤亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.45,0:13:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暴露和平主义的不设防
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.73,0:13:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自私自利\N帕根，我要去现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请快点准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.71,0:13:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很危险的\N请莉莉娜小姐三思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.48,0:13:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要直接去制止他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有那办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现场有战斗很混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新生OZ会令那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.52,0:13:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变成炼狱般的地区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.32,0:13:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道他们为了什么发动战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是说我是他们的目标呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但有什么结果也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.69,0:14:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在重要的是制止他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.57,0:14:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.54,0:14:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下!快点快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.31,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.28,0:14:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平主义国家不可以有的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把宇宙用机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改良为陆战用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.32,0:14:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主知道这件事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.96,0:14:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为有这种力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.13,0:14:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类才会想要战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.83,0:14:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为他们想紧紧抱着\N玻璃手工艺般脆弱的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她一定会那样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.20,0:14:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，现在才一定要战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.54,0:14:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛的行动\N一定对山克王国有益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们用这些陶拉斯追上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.48,0:14:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我去准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,装置完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.79,0:15:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.79,0:15:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然不能从这国家撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.66,0:15:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降下的MD果然是想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我们赶进山克王国的中心部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.70,0:15:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.87,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上把本部队的一切炸毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.71,0:15:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个小孩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.72,0:15:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你们既然打算\N为了这国家而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们的性命就还有一点用处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.52,0:15:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的用处?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们打算保护这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不设防的国家吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.46,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们没剩下多少的军力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.13,0:15:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若想向罗姆斐拉反击\N那就跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.77,0:15:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺利的话，或许能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.74,0:16:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这国家对我有恩，只是那样而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，派两三人跟我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长!你相信他吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.05,0:16:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有多少人认为\N能打赢MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.32,0:16:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是罗姆斐拉害怕的那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.69,0:16:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么\N那少年是钢弹驾驶员吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比想像中更没趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.92,0:16:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，部份特列斯派已经被消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但推测本队前去市区了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上转为追击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.33,0:16:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来历不明飞机正急速接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.33,0:16:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.74,0:17:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是对空战，我们暂时有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.77,0:17:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下你曾见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的战场吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不大想踏上战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.51,0:17:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为人会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁也不想死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，战斗的人是拼命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.16,0:17:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得那方面好有魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的会好紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.20,0:18:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想感谢出生于这时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些白色机体是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.97,0:18:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,属于哪个国家的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来历不明的机动战士运输机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正冲过来   什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向MD发出指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.25,0:18:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!击落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无谓的挣扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…?   钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.18,0:18:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危险!桃乐丝!停车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.11,0:19:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝，没事吧?  桃乐丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国不需要这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.88,0:19:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下你会那样说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.91,0:19:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但罗姆斐拉的行动\N正逐渐形成压力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.48,0:19:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.65,0:20:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我违反了莉莉娜殿下你的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.65,0:20:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我认为没防卫力量会被击败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这全是我的主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愿接受任何处分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.83,0:20:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不用反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和罗姆斐拉财团正面战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.80,0:20:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这程度的战斗力实在太少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.00,0:20:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以坐以待毙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.97,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像过去的领导人一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.64,0:20:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的思想是梦想\N还是错误呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团会陆续消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妨碍他们的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙卫星，钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.99,0:20:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已经成为代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.96,0:20:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要战斗消灭他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，拒绝战斗的态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.77,0:20:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形成财团现在的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时代急速改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.44,0:20:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉的焦急\N是这场战争的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.64,0:20:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主义吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.11,0:21:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界正朝着那方向前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.85,0:21:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也要明白诺茵的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.45,0:21:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在须要防卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.52,0:21:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了能拥有讨论的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.12,0:21:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!你去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.25,0:21:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搜索特洛瓦的人情我已经还了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.59,0:21:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会照自己的意思行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的脑内没有和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.56,0:21:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹是为了战斗而存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会怎样管治山克王国?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.60,0:21:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和诺茵一样，创立防卫部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.74,0:21:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.81,0:21:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最能抗衡罗姆斐拉的方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.41,0:21:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，诺茵小姐，我批准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.45,0:21:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请照你们的意思行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.05,0:21:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我和我身边的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.65,0:21:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能意见一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.75,0:21:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能令全世界有同一想法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.72,0:21:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我终有一日会找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.19,0:21:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么驱使大家战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.01,0:22:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.04,0:22:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她绝对不是输给钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.11,0:22:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我好喜欢莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.45,0:22:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.00,0:22:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.00,0:22:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.00,0:22:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.00,0:22:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.50,0:22:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.00,0:23:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.00,0:23:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.19,0:23:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回予告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.73,0:23:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降落地球的希洛和卡特尔以外的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.13,0:23:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹驾驶员停留在宇宙
